{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"CSSStyleDeclaration.removeProperty()","mdn_url":"/ja/docs/Web/API/CSSStyleDeclaration/removeProperty","locale":"ja","native":"日本語","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/CSS_Object_Model\">CSS Object Model</a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/CSSStyleDeclaration\"><code>CSSStyleDeclaration</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>プロパティ</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/CSSStyleDeclaration/length\"><code>length</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/CSSStyleDeclaration/parentRule\"><code>parentRule</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>メソッド</summary><ol><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/CSSStyleDeclaration/getPropertyCSSValue\"><code>getPropertyCSSValue()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/CSSStyleDeclaration/getPropertyPriority\"><code>getPropertyPriority()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/CSSStyleDeclaration/getPropertyValue\"><code>getPropertyValue()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/CSSStyleDeclaration/item\"><code>item()</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSStyleDeclaration/msGetPropertyEnabled\"><code>msGetPropertyEnabled()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSStyleDeclaration/msPutPropertyEnabled\"><code>msPutPropertyEnabled()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><em><code>removeProperty()</code></em></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/CSSStyleDeclaration/setProperty\"><code>setProperty()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>CSSOM に関連するページ</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/AnimationEvent\"><code>AnimationEvent</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/CSS\"><code>CSS</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/CSSConditionRule\"><code>CSSConditionRule</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/CSSGroupingRule\"><code>CSSGroupingRule</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/CSSKeyframeRule\"><code>CSSKeyframeRule</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/CSSKeyframesRule\"><code>CSSKeyframesRule</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/CSSMediaRule\"><code>CSSMediaRule</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSNamespaceRule\"><code>CSSNamespaceRule</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/CSSPageRule\"><code>CSSPageRule</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/CSSRule\"><code>CSSRule</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/CSSRuleList\"><code>CSSRuleList</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/CSSStyleRule\"><code>CSSStyleRule</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/CSSStyleSheet\"><code>CSSStyleSheet</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/CSSSupportsRule\"><code>CSSSupportsRule</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/CaretPosition\"><code>CaretPosition</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/MediaQueryList\"><code>MediaQueryList</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Screen\"><code>Screen</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/StyleSheet\"><code>StyleSheet</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/StyleSheetList\"><code>StyleSheetList</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/TransitionEvent\"><code>TransitionEvent</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>\n\n<p><strong><code>CSSStyleDeclaration.removeProperty()</code></strong>&nbsp;メソッドインターフェイスは、 CSS スタイル宣言オブジェクトからプロパティを削除します。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"構文","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> oldValue <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> style<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">removeProperty</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>property<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"parameters","title":"引数","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><em><code>property</code></em> は <a href=\"/ja/docs/conflicting/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String_6fa58bba0570d663099f0ae7ae8883ab\"><code>DOMString</code></a>&nbsp;で、削除するプロパティ名を表します。なお、複数語からなるプロパティ名はハイフン区切りであって、キャメルケースではありません。</li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"return_value","title":"返値","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><code><em>oldValue</em></code> は <a href=\"/ja/docs/conflicting/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String_6fa58bba0570d663099f0ae7ae8883ab\"><code>DOMString</code></a> で、削除される前の CSS プロパティの値と等しいものです。</li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"exceptions","title":"例外","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/DOMException\"><code>DOMException</code></a>&nbsp;NO_MODIFICATION_ALLOWED_ERR: プロパティまたは宣言ブロックが読取専用の場合。</li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"example","title":"例","isH3":false,"content":"<p>次の JavaScript コードは、 CSS の <code>background-color</code>&nbsp;プロパティをセレクター規則から削除します。</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> declaration <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>styleSheets<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>rules<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>style<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> oldValue <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> declaration<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">removeProperty</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'background-color'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"仕様書","id":"specifications","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://drafts.csswg.org/cssom/#dom-cssstyledeclaration-removeproperty","title":"CSS Object Model (CSSOM)"}],"query":"api.CSSStyleDeclaration.removeProperty"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"ブラウザーの互換性","id":"browser_compatibility","isH3":false,"query":"api.CSSStyleDeclaration.removeProperty","dataURL":"/ja/docs/Web/API/CSSStyleDeclaration/removeProperty/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"構文","id":"syntax"},{"text":"例","id":"example"},{"text":"仕様書","id":"specifications"},{"text":"ブラウザーの互換性","id":"browser_compatibility"}],"summary":"CSSStyleDeclaration.removeProperty() メソッドインターフェイスは、 CSS スタイル宣言オブジェクトからプロパティを削除します。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"CSSStyleDeclaration.removeProperty()","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"CSSStyleDeclaration.removeProperty()","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"ja/web/api/cssstyledeclaration/removeproperty","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/ja/web/api/cssstyledeclaration/removeproperty/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web","title":"開発者向けのウェブ技術"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/API/CSSStyleDeclaration","title":"CSSStyleDeclaration"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/API/CSSStyleDeclaration/removeProperty","title":"CSSStyleDeclaration.removeProperty()"}],"pageTitle":"CSSStyleDeclaration.removeProperty() - Web API | MDN","noIndexing":false}}